{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium mobile-first ingredient spotlight section for Ariya Supplements’ sleep product, Calm Nights.
    
    The section should feel clean, modern, educational, and premium while maintaining a luxury wellness aesthetic similar to leading DTC wellness brands.
    
    Section Headline
    Inside Calm Nights
    
    Supporting Text
    Every ingredient was chosen for a reason. No proprietary blends. No hidden doses.
    
    Layout Requirements
    Use an interactive accordion-style layout.
    Each ingredient should appear as its own expandable card.
    When tapped, the card expands to reveal a short explanation.
    Rounded corners.
    Plenty of white space.
    Mobile-first design.
    Clean typography.
    Smooth expand/collapse animations.
    Educational but easy to understand.
    Avoid scientific jargon and long paragraphs.
    Keep the section highly scannable.
    Ingredient 1
    L-Theanine
    
    Benefit Title: Calm The Mind
    
    Description: Promotes a relaxed mental state and helps quiet racing thoughts before bed.
    
    Ingredient 2
    L-Tryptophan
    
    Benefit Title: Fall Asleep Naturally
    
    Description: An amino acid your body uses to support natural sleep pathways and nighttime relaxation.
    
    Ingredient 3
    Lemon Balm Extract
    
    Benefit Title: Ease Stress
    
    Description: Traditionally used to support relaxation and help unwind after a long day.
    
    Ingredient 4
    Chamomile Extract
    
    Benefit Title: Support Relaxation
    
    Description: Contains naturally occurring compounds that help prepare the body for sleep.
    
    Ingredient 5
    Tart Cherry Extract
    
    Benefit Title: Sleep Quality Support
    
    Description: Supports healthy sleep quality and overnight recovery.
    
    Color & Visual Direction
    Use color intentionally and sparingly.
    
    Do NOT make the entire section purple.
    
    Maintain a premium luxury wellness aesthetic.
    
    Ingredient Color Coordination
    L-Theanine → Soft green accents
    L-Tryptophan → Ariya purple accents
    Lemon Balm → Sage green accents
    Chamomile → Soft golden yellow accents
    Tart Cherry → Deep cherry red accents
    Design Rules
    Ingredient names should be dark charcoal or black.
    Benefit titles should use the ingredient accent color.
    Background should remain white.
    Cards should be white with subtle shadows.
    Use accent colors only for icons, active accordion states, and benefit titles.
    Avoid large blocks of color.
    Keep the overall section clean, minimal, and easy to read.
    Goal
    Help customers understand why each ingredient is included in the formula while reinforcing Ariya’s commitment to transparency, fully disclosed ingredients, and a thoughtfully designed melatonin-free sleep formula.
    
    The section should feel premium, trustworthy, educational, and visually consistent with the rest of the Calm Nights product page.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-ingredient-spotlight-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_mobile }}px 20px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: {{ block.settings.text_alignment }};
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size_mobile }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.headline_color }};
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__subtext-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subtext_size_mobile }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtext_color }};
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 600px;
    {% if block.settings.text_alignment == 'center' %}
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__accordion-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: {{ block.settings.card_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    box-shadow: {{ block.settings.card_shadow }};
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active .ai-ingredient-spotlight__icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 60%;
    height: 60%;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-title-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__ingredient-name-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.ingredient_name_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.ingredient_name_color }};
    margin: 0 0 2px 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__benefit-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.benefit_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__chevron-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    color: {{ block.settings.chevron_color }};
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active .ai-ingredient-spotlight__chevron-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease, padding 0.4s ease;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-height: 500px;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 0 {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.description_color }};
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-ingredient-spotlight-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_desktop }}px 40px;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__subtext-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subtext_size_desktop }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

